OL,3,CKing's congress address was the words
OL,4,Cof a 'wise friend' ` Lionel Richie
OL,6,FSuperstar singer Lionel Richie has
OL,7,Fpraised the King's speech to the US
OL,8,FCongress, describing Charles as a wise
OL,9,Ffriend "giving advice as to what we
OL,10,Fshould be doing".
OL,12,FRichie was among a host of celebrity
OL,13,Fsupporters of the King's Trust who
OL,14,Fjoined its founder and the Queen on
OL,15,FWednesday to celebrate the charity's
OL,16,Fwork and showcase the UK's cultural
OL,17,Fimpact on New York.
OL,26,@qD@HOUrD@PO]
