OL,3,CKing's congress address was the words
OL,4,Cof a 'wise friend' ` Lionel Richie
OL,6,FThe gathering of stars, which included
OL,7,FItalian fashion designer Donatella
OL,8,FVersace, fashion guru Anna Wintour,
OL,9,FBritish creative Stella McCartney and
OL,10,Fmodel Iman, came at the end of a
OL,11,Fwhirlwind royal day in Manhattan.
OL,13,FThe King and Queen began by declaring
OL,14,Fthey stood "in enduring solidarity
OL,15,Fwith the American people" when they
OL,16,Fcommemorated those killed during the
OL,17,FSeptember 11 terrorist attacks.
OL,26,@vD@LOUwD@YO]
