OL,3,CKing's congress address was the words
OL,4,Cof a 'wise friend' ` Lionel Richie
OL,6,FCharles and Camilla's words of
OL,7,Fsympathy were written in a message
OL,8,Fleft with a bouquet of flowers placed
OL,9,Fat the imposing memorial in New York,
OL,10,Fhonouring the thousands of people who
OL,11,Flost their lives almost 25 years ago.
OL,13,FIn contrast to the poignant moment,
OL,14,Fthe Queen later met Sex and the City
OL,15,Fstar Sarah Jessica Parker at an event
OL,16,Fcelebrating literature at the New York
OL,17,FPublic Library, with the actress
OL,18,Fsaying Camilla's visit was "great for
OL,19,Fall New Yorkers".
OL,26,@zD@\OU{D@PO]
