OL,3,CKing's congress address was the words
OL,4,Cof a 'wise friend' ` Lionel Richie
OL,6,FRichie, the first global ambassador
OL,7,Fand chairman of the Global Ambassador
OL,8,FGroup for the King's Trust, said about
OL,9,FCharles' address on Tuesday on Capitol
OL,10,FHill: "I thought it was brilliant and
OL,11,Fhow he threaded the needle ` so
OL,12,Fbrilliant, but brought us back into
OL,13,Fhumanity as only he can do
OL,15,F"A friend, giving advice as to what we
OL,16,Fshould be doing, a wise friend."
OL,26,@rD@GOUwD@AOUxD@`O]
