OL,3,CKing's congress address was the words
OL,4,Cof a 'wise friend' ` Lionel Richie
OL,6,FCharles has been praised for his
OL,7,Fspeech which outlined the issues,
OL,8,Fvalues and priorities important to the
OL,9,FUK and many of its allies, from
OL,10,Fsupport for Ukraine to the threat to
OL,11,Fthe environment and the importance of
OL,12,Fthe rule of law.
OL,14,FThe New York Times said: "Beneath King
OL,15,FCharles's jokes and decorum, some
OL,16,Fsubtle rebuttals to Trump, King
OL,17,FCharles III gently pushed back against
OL,18,FPresident Trump's attacks on Britain
OL,19,Fand Nato, and he spoke of the
OL,20,Fimportance of checks and balances."
OL,26,@vD@ZOU|D@cO]
