OL,3,CKing's congress address was the words
OL,4,Cof a 'wise friend' ` Lionel Richie
OL,6,FDuring the reception at Christie's
OL,7,Fauction house, Charles began by making
OL,8,Fthe audience laugh when he told them:
OL,9,F"I hesitate to make another speech
OL,10,Fbecause I may have had enough".
OL,12,FThe monarch, who has cancer, joked "as
OL,13,Fwe look to the future, I won't see the
OL,14,Flong-distance future" and he urged
OL,15,Fthose in the room to "champion the
OL,16,Fnext generation".
