OL,3,CKing's congress address was the words
OL,4,Cof a 'wise friend' ` Lionel Richie
OL,6,FCharles and Camilla will end their
OL,7,Ffour-day state visit, the King's first
OL,8,Ftrip to the US as monarch, on Thursday
OL,9,Fby marking the 250th anniversary of US
OL,10,Findependence.
OL,12,FThe royal couple will travel to
OL,13,FVirginia to join residents at a "block-
OL,14,Fparty" featuring food and
OL,15,Fentertainment to celebrate America,
OL,16,Fthe creation of the nation's Founding
OL,17,FFathers described by Charles in his
OL,18,FCongress address as "bold and
OL,19,Fimaginative rebels with a cause".
OL,26,@uD@aOUvD@FO]zD@UOU{D@`O]
