OL,3,CKing's congress address was the words
OL,4,Cof a 'wise friend' ` Lionel Richie
OL,6,FIn one of America's national parks,
OL,7,Fthe King will meet one of the area's
OL,8,Findigenous communities and people
OL,9,Finvolved in conservation initiatives
OL,10,Fand efforts to protect the natural
OL,11,Fenvironment.
OL,13,FSeparately, the Queen will visit a
OL,14,Ffarm to highlight the work of
OL,15,FAmerica's horse racing industry and
OL,16,Fthe long-term links with the sport in
OL,17,Fthe UK.
OL,19,FIn a rare interview, the Queen said
OL,20,Fthe trip had been "wonderful".
OL,26,@|D@SOU|D@]O]
