OL,6,FSpeaking to NBC, in an interview to be
OL,7,Fbroadcast in the US on Thursday,
OL,8,FCamilla told Jenna Bush Hager:
OL,9,F"Everybody's been very kind and
OL,10,Fwelcoming."
